本的新版本再重新套用變更。','Update your theme to the latest version. If no update is available contact your theme author asking about compatibility with the current WooCommerce version.'=>'將佈景主題更新至最新版本。如果沒有可用的更新，請聯絡你的佈景主題作者，詢問與最新 WooCommerce 版本的相容性。','Your {site_title} account has been created!'=>'已建立你的 {site_title} 帳戶！','Amount of coupons.'=>'優惠券數。','Coupon type name.'=>'優惠券類型名稱。','WooCommerce PayPal Checkout Gateway'=>'WooCommerce PayPal 結帳閘道','Low stock amount'=>'低庫存量','ShipStation'=>'ShipStation','ShipStation icon'=>'ShipStation 圖示','Export all categories'=>'匯出所有分類','<strong>Your theme (%s) contains outdated copies of some WooCommerce template files.</strong> These files may need updating to ensure they are compatible with the current version of WooCommerce. Suggestions to fix this:'=>'<strong>你的佈景主題 (%s) 包含一些已過時的 WooCommerce 範本檔案副本。</strong>你可能需要更新這些檔案以確保與 WooCommerce 的最新版本相容。修正此問題的建議方式：','Which product category should be exported?'=>'應匯出哪個商品分類？','This is the attachment ID, or image URL, used for placeholder images in the product catalog. Products with no image will use this.'=>'這是附件 ID (或圖片 URL)，用於商品目錄中的預留位置圖片。沒有圖片的商品將會使用此圖。','Enter attachment ID or URL to an image'=>'輸入附件 ID 或圖片 URL','Placeholder image'=>'預留位置圖片','The "%s" payment method is currently disabled'=>'「%s」付款方式目前已停用','The "%s" payment method is currently enabled'=>'「%s」付款方式目前已啟用','Set up the "%s" payment method'=>'設定「%s」付款方式','Manage the "%s" payment method'=>'管理「%s」付款方式','Move down'=>'向下移動','Move the "%s" payment method down'=>'向下移動「%s」付款方式','Move up'=>'向上移動','Move the "%s" payment method up'=>'向上移動「%s」付款方式','When handling an %s, should access to downloadable files be revoked and download logs cleared?'=>'處理%s時，是否會撤銷可下載檔案的存取權限並清除下載記錄？','When handling an %s, should personal data within orders be retained or removed?'=>'處理%s時，是否會保留或是移除訂單中的個人資料？','Enter a number to set stock quantity at the variation level. Use a variation\'s \'Manage stock?\' check box above to enable/disable stock management at the variation level.'=>'輸入數字以設定變化版本層級的庫存數量。使用上方變化版本的「管理庫存？」核取方塊來啟用/停用變化版本層級的庫存管理功能。','Set up PayPal for me using this email:'=>'使用此電子郵件為我設定 PayPal：','Set up Stripe for me using this email:'=>'使用此電子郵件為我設定 Stripe：','We\'ll use %1$s for product weight and %2$s for product dimensions.'=>'我們的商品重量採用%1$s，商品尺寸採用%2$s。','We recommend using ShipStation to save time at the post office by printing your shipping labels at home. Try ShipStation free for 30 days.'=>'建議你在家使用 ShipStation 列印郵寄標籤，省下在郵局處理包裹的時間。免費試用 ShipStation 30 天。','WooCommerce Services icon'=>'WooCommerce 服務圖示','A live rate is the exact cost to ship an order, quoted directly from the shipping carrier.'=>'即時費率是直接由運輸業者報價的訂單實際運費。','If you\'d like to offer <span class="help_tip" data-tip="%1$s">live rates</span> from a specific carrier (e.g. UPS) you can find a variety of extensions available for WooCommerce <a href="%2$s" target="_blank">here</a>.'=>'若你想提供特定運輸業者 (例如 UPS) 的<span class="help_tip" data-tip="%1$s">即時費率</span>，可以在<a href="%2$s" target="_blank">這裡</a>尋找 WooCommerce 可用的各種擴充功能。','We\'ve created two Shipping Zones - for %s and for the rest of the world. Below you can set Flat Rate shipping costs for these Zones or offer Free Shipping.'=>'我們建立了兩個運送區域，分別為%s和全球其餘區域。你可在下方為這些區域設定固定運費或提供免運費服務。','Kilograms'=>'公斤','Pounds'=>'磅','Grams'=>'克','Yards'=>'英碼','Inches'=>'英寸','Millimeters'=>'公釐','Centimeters'=>'公分','Meters'=>'公尺','Ounces'=>'盎司','Item moved down'=>'商品已向下移動','Item moved up'=>'商品已向上移動','You may need to manually restore the item\'s stock.'=>'你可能需要手動還原該商品的庫存。','Are you sure you want to remove the selected items?'=>'你確定要移除選取的商品？','Alto Paraguay'=>'Alto Paraguay','Presidente Hayes'=>'Presidente Hayes','Amambay'=>'Amambay','Central'=>'Central','Cordillera'=>'Cordillera','San Pedro'=>'San Pedro','Sud Sardegna'=>'Sud Sardegna','%d API key permanently revoked.'=>'%d API 金鑰已永久撤銷。','Apartment, suite, unit, etc.'=>'公寓、套房、單位等','This action cannot be reversed. Are you sure you wish to erase personal data from the selected orders?'=>'此動作無法復原。