 WooCommerce 結帳頁面的外觀。','I have read and agree to the website %s'=>'我已閱讀並同意網站的 %s','Take payments in person via checks. This offline gateway can also be useful to test purchases.'=>'透過支票親自收款。這個離線閘道亦可用於測試購買項目，相當實用。','Take payments in person via BACS. More commonly known as direct bank/wire transfer.'=>'透過 BACS 親自收款。 更常見的說法是銀行/轉帳/電匯。','Please see the <a href="https://www.paypal.com/us/webapps/mpp/ua/privacy-full">PayPal Privacy Policy</a> for more details.'=>'請參閱 <a href="https://www.paypal.com/us/webapps/mpp/ua/privacy-full">PayPal 隱私權政策</a>以取得更多詳細資料。','We accept payments through PayPal. When processing payments, some of your data will be passed to PayPal, including information required to process or support the payment, such as the purchase total and billing information.'=>'我們接受透過 PayPal 付款。處理付款時，會將你的部分資料傳送給 PayPal，包括處理或支援付款所需的資訊 (例如購買總金額和帳單資訊)。','Account details:'=>'帳戶詳細資料：','In this subsection you should list which third party payment processors you’re using to take payments on your store since these may handle customer data. We’ve included PayPal as an example, but you should remove this if you’re not using PayPal.'=>'你應該在此次區段中列出你的商店用來接受付款的第三方付款處理單位，因為這些單位可能會涉及客戶資料處理。我們已將 PayPal 加入做為範例，但如果你並未使用 PayPal，請移除此項目。','In this section you should list who you’re sharing data with, and for what purpose. This could include, but may not be limited to, analytics, marketing, payment gateways, shipping providers, and third party embeds.'=>'你應在此區段中列出你共用資訊的對象與目的。這可能包括但不限於分析、行銷、付款閘道、貨運供應商及第三方嵌入項目。','We share information with third parties who help us provide our orders and store services to you; for example --'=>'我們會與協助我們提供你訂單和商店服務的第三方共用資訊；例如：','Members of our team have access to the information you provide us. For example, both Administrators and Shop Managers can access:'=>'我們的團隊成員可存取你提供給我們的資料。例如，管理員和商店經理均可存取以下資料：','Order information like what was purchased, when it was purchased and where it should be sent, and'=>'購買項目、時間和傳送目的地等訂購資訊，以及','Our team members have access to this information to help fulfill orders, process refunds and support you.'=>'我們的團隊成員可存取此資訊以協助履行訂單、處理退款和為你提供支援。','What we share with others'=>'我們與他人共用的項目','Who on our team has access'=>'擁有存取權的團隊成員','Customer information like your name, email address, and billing and shipping information.'=>'你的姓名、電子郵件地址以及帳單和運送資料等客戶資訊。','We will also store comments or reviews, if you choose to leave them.'=>'如果你選擇留下留言和評論，我們也會儲存這些內容。','We generally store information about you for as long as we need the information for the purposes for which we collect and use it, and we are not legally required to continue to keep it. For example, we will store order information for XXX years for tax and accounting purposes. This includes your name, email address and billing and shipping addresses.'=>'我們通常只會在出於收集和使用的目的而需要這些資訊時，才會儲存有關你的資訊，在法律上我們並不需要繼續保留這些資訊。例如，我們會為了稅務和會計目的而儲存訂單資訊 XXX 年。這包括你的姓名、電子郵件地址以及帳單和運送地址。','Comply with any legal obligations we have, such as calculating taxes'=>'遵循法律義務，例如計算稅額','Improve our store offerings'=>'改善商店優惠內容','Process payments and prevent fraud'=>'處理付款和防範詐騙','Respond to your requests, including refunds and complaints'=>'回覆你的申請，包括退款要求或客訴。','Send you marketing messages, if you choose to receive them'=>'傳送行銷訊息給你 (如果你已同意接收)','If you create an account, we will store your name, address, email and phone number, which will be used to populate the checkout for future orders.'=>'如果你建立帳戶，我們將會儲存你的姓名、地址、電子郵件和電話號碼，以便在日後用於訂單自動填入結帳資訊。','Set up your account for our store'=>'開設你在我們商店的帳戶','Send you information about your account and order'=>'將帳戶和訂單相關資訊傳送給你','When you purchase from us, we’ll ask you to provide information including your name, billing address, shipping address, email address, phone number, credit card/payment details and optional account information like username and password. We’ll use this information for purposes, such as, to:'=>'當你向我們購買產品時，我們會要求你提供一些資訊，包括你的姓名、帳單地址、運送地址、電子郵件地址、電話號碼、信用卡/付款詳細資料以及選填的帳戶資訊 (例如使用者名稱和密碼)。我們會將這個資訊用於以下的用途，例如：','We’ll also use cookies to keep track of cart contents while you’re browsing our site.'=>'我們也會使用 Cookie 來追蹤你在瀏覽我們網站時的購物車內容。','Note: you may want to further detail your cookie policy, and link to that section from here.'=>'附註：你可能想要進一步瞭解 Cookie 政策，請從這裡連結至該區段。','Shipping address: we’ll ask you to enter this so we can, for instance, estimate shipping before you place an order, and send you the order!'=>'運送地址：舉例來說，我們會要求你輸入運送地址，以便在你下訂單前估算運費，然後將訂單傳送給你！','Location, IP address and browser type: we’ll use this for purposes like estimating taxes and shipping'=>'位置、IP 位址和瀏覽器類型：我們會利用此資訊來估算稅額和運費','Products you’ve viewed: we’ll use this to, for example, show you products you’ve recently viewed'=>'你已檢視過的產品：例如，我們會運用此資訊來顯示你最近瀏覽過的產品。','We collect information about you during the checkout process on our store.'=>'你在我們商店中進行結帳的過程中，我們會收集你的相關資訊。','What we collect and store'=>'我們收集和儲存的內容','While you visit our site, we’ll track:'=>'在你造訪我們的網站時，我們會追蹤以下項目：','This sample language includes the basics around what personal data your store may be collecting, storing and sharing, as well as who may have access to that data. Depending on what settings are enabled and which additional plugins are used, the specific information shared by your store will vary. We recommend consulting with a lawyer when deciding what information to disclose on your privacy policy.'=>'此範例語言包括你的商店可能正在收集、儲存和共用哪些個人資料以及誰可以存取該資料等基本資訊。視啟用的設定以及使用的外掛程式而定，你的商店所分享的具體資訊內容可能會有所不同。我們建議你決定在隱私權政策中揭露哪些資訊前，請先諮詢律師。','Order Number'=>'訂單號碼','Access granted'=>'已授予存取權','Browser User Agent'=>'瀏覽器使用者代理程式','Download count'=>'下載計數','Items Purchased'=>'已購買的項目','Token'=>'代碼','Payment Tokens'=>'付款代碼','User email'=>'使用者電子郵件地址','Personal data removed.'=>'個人資料已移除。','User roleCustomer'=>'客戶','Display name'=>'顯示名稱','display name%1$s %2$s'=>'%1$s %2$s','%1$s has been removed from your cart because it has since been modified. You can add it back to your cart <a href="%2$s">here</a>.'=>'%1$s 已修改，因此已從你的購物車中移除。你可以在<a href="%2$s">這裡</a>將它重新放入購物車。','%d permissions deleted'=>'已刪除的 %d 權限','Access to Purchased Do